{"tid":2029247,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港版國安法：草案內容指國安機關可在港成立機構","createTime":"2020-05-22T06:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T10:39:58.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c055a525a4a64423b94b684dd0f9bcb4dafd5e11","tid":2029247,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:55:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/港版國安法草案內容指國安機關可在港成立機構-033842362.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9%E6%8C%87%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%A9%9F%E9%97%9C%E5%8F%AF%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%AF%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B-033842362.html&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSr%2FjevXO%2BySp3REELKrGah4%3D&h=6fa0c893\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/港版國安法草案內容指國安機關可在港成立機構-033842362.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ksApIhWbjd7NzMTGBn8qcw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDQx/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-05/b183e430-9bdd-11ea-9f77-658e4dc640c5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FksApIhWbjd7NzMTGBn8qcw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDQx%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-05%2Fb183e430-9bdd-11ea-9f77-658e4dc640c5&h=17cd399c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人大常委會副秘書長王晨今早(22日)簡介涉及香港維護國家安全的草案，內容包括中央人民政府維護國家安全的有關機關，根據需要在香港特區建立機構，依法履行維護國家安全相關職責。另外，明確規定香港特別行政區，應當建立健全維護國家安全的機制、機構和執行機制，以及明確規定行政長官，應就特區履行維護國家安全職責，開展國家安全推廣教育，依法禁止危害國家安全的行為等情況，定期向中央政府提交報告。<br />\n<br />\n王晨表示，由於反中亂港及外部敵對力干擾，基本法23條立法自2003年受挫以來，法例在香港被別有用心的人污名、妖魔化，有被長期擱置風險。而有關草案就四方面提出制訂法律防範、制止和懲治，授權人大常委會就建立健全特區維護國家安全、法律制度和執行機制；制定相關法律，切實防範、制止和懲治任何分裂國家、顛覆國家政權、組織實施恐怖活動等嚴重危害國家安全行為，及外國和境外勢力干預特區事務。<br />\n<br />\n王晨補充指，一國兩制在香港實踐過程中遇到新情況，出現新風險、新挑戰，香港的國家安全風險日益突出，特别去年修例風波以來，反中亂港勢力主張獨立，公然污損國旗國徽，圍攻中央駐港機構，暴力對抗警方執法，癱瘓政府立法會。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，近年來外部勢力為香港反中亂港勢力撐腰打氣，有關行為嚴重挑戰一國兩制原則、危害國家主權，因此必須採取有力措施，防範制止和懲治。"},{"pid":"b5ead2ff9a1f3f72f4b489c46ae101a057e125de","tid":2029247,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qRuyyMp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqRuyyMp.jpg&h=fb5f25d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6P4ZujK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6P4ZujK.jpg&h=2fc49f2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75e9f0de1783b3dc419a236eebf5b329fb672826","tid":2029247,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T07:00:46.000Z","msg":"直接架空香港政府"},{"pid":"ce6737d609bfa7677127b545c4cacbe11ed9ce2e","tid":2029247,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T07:12:31.000Z","msg":"即係政治部啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警慌行撚開"},{"pid":"19217017d32a35dd744196ec6fc9681d9a9b5b5b","tid":2029247,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:51:32.000Z","msg":"共產黨肯註冊未？"},{"pid":"ff4ba75141e1043e5aabbe17fc8f42b219d25a01","tid":2029247,"uid":46906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:07:24.000Z","msg":"本身都有解放軍駐軍+啲乜乜辦咩咩辦架啦，直接擴建咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5cc3adb95bc457fee7cb9e6dd0b08273c636b64","tid":2029247,"uid":115096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:14:07.000Z","msg":"國安機構喺高鐵站地底，你都冇佢計。"},{"pid":"de077ea2738f084174a744b315d4e61772b783d2","tid":2029247,"uid":336764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5cc3adb95bc457fee7cb9e6dd0b08273c636b64","tid":2029247,"uid":115096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:14:07.000Z","msg":"國安機構喺高鐵站地底，你都冇佢計。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:38:18.000Z","msg":"根本就一早整好左"},{"pid":"3f325594b99